description:
What goes well with a good murder? Karen and Georgia! We’ve got PART TWO of Unqualified with Karen Kilgariff and Georgia Hardstark (My Favorite Murder). In Part 2, Anna shares the story of actress Rebecca Schaeffer. Then Georgia tells the group about the killer Charlie Brandt and how an early childhood murder led to no good. Later, the gang call Leah, who wants to know if it is okay to hook up with her cheating friend’s ex-husband.
